		<section id="primary">
			<div id="content" role="main">

			
				<header class="page-header">
					<h1 class="page-title">Category Archives: <span>IP</span></h1>

									</header>

				
								
					
	<article id="post-3836" class="post-3836 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-gchq category-intelligence category-ip category-machon category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-privacy-2 category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-talks-2 category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-accountability-2 tag-adviespuntklokkenluiders tag-amsterdam tag-conference tag-free-press-unlimited tag-law-2 tag-privacy tag-surveillance-2 tag-war tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-win">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/keynote-international-whistleblower-conference-amsterdam.html" title="Permalink to Keynote at international whistleblower conference, Amsterdam" rel="bookmark">Keynote at international whistleblower conference, Amsterdam</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/keynote-international-whistleblower-conference-amsterdam.html" title="20:41" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-06-23T20:41:50+00:00" pubdate>June 23, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/keynote-international-whistleblower-conference-amsterdam.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>With thanks to <a href="https://www.freepressunlimited.org/en/article/international-whistleblowers-conference-18-june-2014">Free Press Unlim­ited</a>, the Dutch <a href="http://www.adviespuntklokkenluiders.nl/international">Advice Centre for Whisteblowers</a>, <a href="http://netdem.nl/en/international-whistleblowers-conference-2014/">Net­work Demo­cracy</a>,  and the <a href="http://whistleblowingnetwork.org/2014/05/28/international-whistleblowing-conference-amsterdam-18-june-2014/">Whis­tleblow­ing Inter­na­tional Net­work</a>.</p>
<p>All these organ­isa­tions came together to hold an inter­na­tional con­fer­ence in sup­port of whis­tleblowers on 18<sup>th</sup> June in Amsterdam.</p>
<p>It was a cre­at­ive event, mix­ing up law­yers, journ­al­ists, tech­no­lo­gists and whis­tleblower sup­port net­works from around the world at an event with speeches and work­shops, in order for every­one to learn, share exper­i­ences, and develop new meth­od­o­lo­gies and best prac­tice to help cur­rent and future whistleblowers.</p>
<p>A stim­u­lat­ing and pro­duct­ive day, at which I did the open­ing keynote:</p>
<p><img src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/placeholder_iwc.jpg" alt="placeholder_iwc" width="707" height="397" class="placeholder alignleft size-full wp-image-3840" data-source="vimeo" data-id="98880285" /></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
