	<article id="post-2146" class="post-2146 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-acta category-civil-liberties category-drugs-2 category-intelligence category-ip category-iran category-leap category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-open-source category-radio category-spies category-subversion-2 category-surveillance category-technology category-terrorism category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-anonymous tag-echelon tag-intelligence-2 tag-ip tag-iran tag-kimdotcom tag-leap tag-mega tag-megaupload tag-mi5 tag-mi6-gchq tag-spies-2 tag-subversion tag-terrorism-2 tag-war tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/uk-anonymous-radio-interview.html" title="Permalink to UK Anonymous Radio Interview" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">UK</span> Anonymous Radio Interview</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/uk-anonymous-radio-interview.html" title="23:00" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-02-18T23:00:16+00:00" pubdate>February 18, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/uk-anonymous-radio-interview.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p><a href="https://mega.co.nz/#!2th1QBxY!S3x8OlRoJwOz04Vu8GtdZiIaPOZY_ufKwUmWXvkmedo">Here’s the link </a>to my inter­view tonight on <a href="http://www.spreaker.com/user/anonukire"><span class="caps">UK</span> Anonym­ous Radio</a> — I had a great time and found it a fun, wide-ranging, and stim­u­lat­ing hour.  I hope you do too.  So, thank you Anonymous.</p>
<p>And also thank you to <a href="http://kim.com/">Kim Dot­com</a> set­ting up the new file-sharing site, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mega_%28website%29">Mega</a>, which replaces his <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/11/asymmetric-extradition-the-american-way.html">illegally-taken-down global site</a>, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Megaupload">MegaUp­load</a>.  I have some­where safe, I think, to store my interviews!</p>
<p>What a sham­bolic dis­grace that MegaUp­load raid was, and what a clas­sic example of the global cor­por­at­ist agenda that I dis­cuss in the interview.</p>
<p>I do love geeks.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
