	<article id="post-2255" class="post-2255 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-extradition category-gchq category-intelligence category-ip category-it category-law category-media category-nsa category-politics category-spies category-surveillance category-technology category-tv tag-annie-machon tag-big-brother tag-corbett-report tag-echelon tag-extradition-2 tag-fisa tag-free-media tag-kim-dotcom tag-richard-odwyer tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/the-fisa-echelon-panopticon.html" title="Permalink to The FISA/Echelon Panopticon" rel="bookmark">The <span class="caps">FISA</span>/Echelon Panopticon</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/the-fisa-echelon-panopticon.html" title="20:20" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-02-15T20:20:00+00:00" pubdate>February 15, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/the-fisa-echelon-panopticon.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>A recent inter­view with James Corbett of the <a href="http://www.corbettreport.com/">Corbett Report</a> on <a href="http://grtv.ca/2013/02/death-privacy-inside-fisaechelon-spy-grid">Global Research <span class="caps">TV</span> </a>dis­cuss­ing issues such as <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foreign_Intelligence_Surveillance_Act"><span class="caps">FISA</span></a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/echelon-redux.html">Ech­elon</a>, and our cul­tural “groom­ing” by the bur­geon­ing sur­veil­lance state:<br />
<iframe src="http://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/mYmc9RqQ8pA" height="315" width="560" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/the-fisa-echelon-panopticon.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/big-brother" title="View all posts in Big Brother" rel="category tag">Big Brother</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/extradition" title="View all posts in Extradition" rel="category tag">Extradition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/gchq" title="View all posts in GCHQ" rel="category tag">GCHQ</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/ip" title="View all posts in IP" rel="category tag">IP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/it" title="View all posts in IT" rel="category tag">IT</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/media" title="View all posts in Media" rel="category tag">Media</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/nsa" title="View all posts in NSA" rel="category tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/surveillance" title="View all posts in Surveillance" rel="category tag">Surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/technology" title="View all posts in Technology" rel="catego